Physics 1, OCR &#039;Physics A&#039; A level textbook [scanned]

This textbook covers the three AS modules of the OCR &#039;Physics A&#039; A level, Forces and Motion [2821], Electrons and Photons [2822], and Wave Properties [2823]. Note that this is the &#039;old&#039; specification, i.e. not the specification being introduced in 2008.  
Although written for the OCR &#039;Physics A&#039; A Level, it may be of use to anyone studying at that sort of level (16-18yrs).


Author: David Sang, Keith Gibbs & Robert Hutchings

Publisher: Cambridge University Press (United Kingdom)

Year: 2000

ISBN-13: 9780521787185
